                                                    Check-In : <span class="badge" style="background:none;color:black;">@HotelDetailedVM.CheckInDate</span>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class="list-group-item">
                                                    Check-Out : <span class="badge" style="background:none;color:black;">@HotelDetailedVM.CheckOutDate</span>
